short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extraheer profiel(en) naar je  Recruiter XL applicatie.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This an extension to parse profiles to (ATS) Recruiter XL.
This extension provides an easy way for end users of Recruiter XL to parse the found candidate profiles from various CV databases to the ATS Recruiter XL. If you have installed the extension and then open the extension, you will immediately see all the possibilities.

Extension makes it possible to parse multiple candidate profiles at the same time. You can use this extension in multiple browser tabs to search different CV databases for suitable candidates and easily add suitable candidates to the parse list. After you finish adding all candidates on various pages, click on the Bulk Parse option to process the selected/added candidates all at once
